<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 15:14:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于竞争损害需求，特斯拉年度交付量首次下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-posts-first-fall-annual-deliveries-demand-slows-2025-01-02/</link><description>特斯拉周四公布年度交付量首次下降，原因是该汽车制造商第四季度交付的电动汽车数量低于预期，而且激励措施未能提振对其老化车型系列的需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 14:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-posts-first-fall-annual-deliveries-demand-slows-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>钴矿商 Jervois 在与中国竞争困难后达成救援协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cobalt-miner-jervois-rescue-deal-after-struggle-compete-with-china-2025-01-02/</link><description>电池金属钴价格暴跌迫使新兴生产商Jervois Global Ltd退市并进行重组，该公司在与中国竞争对手竞争多年后于周四表示。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 13:07:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/cobalt-miner-jervois-rescue-deal-after-struggle-compete-with-china-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车在挪威获得市场份额</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicles-gain-market-share-norway-2025-01-02/</link><description>挪威公路联合会 (OFV) 周四的数据显示，仅五年时间，中国电动汽车就已飙升至挪威新车销量的近 10%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 11:46:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicles-gain-market-share-norway-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：今年第一个交易日，需谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-02/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 11:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑制定限制或禁止中国无人机的潜在规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</link><description>美国商务部周四表示，正在考虑制定新规则，对中国无人机实施限制，以国家安全考虑为由限制或禁止中国无人机在美国销售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 10:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-considers-potential-rules-restrict-or-bar-chinese-drones-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>价格战进入第三年，中国电动汽车制造商扩大购买激励措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-extend-buying-incentives-price-war-enters-third-year-2025-01-02/</link><description>随着全球最大汽车市场的价格战持续第三年，包括蔚来汽车和理想汽车在内的中国电动汽车制造商效仿市场领导者特斯拉和比亚迪，将购买激励措施延长至 2025 年初。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 10:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-makers-extend-buying-incentives-price-war-enters-third-year-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国将28家美国实体列入出口管制名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adds-28-us-entities-export-control-list-2025-01-02/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国已将 28 家美国实体列入出口管制清单，以“维护国家安全和利益”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 08:21:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/china-adds-28-us-entities-export-control-list-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>随着竞争加剧，苹果在中国提供 iPhone 折扣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-discounts-china-competition-intensifies-2025-01-02/</link><description>苹果在中国为其最新款 iPhone 机型提供罕见的高达 500 元人民币的折扣，这家美国科技巨头正在采取行动，抵御来自华为等国内竞争对手日益激烈的竞争，以捍卫自己的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:57:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-offers-iphone-discounts-china-competition-intensifies-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫健委将缩小精神卫生服务差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</link><description>中国国家卫生健康委员会表示，随着当局努力解决越来越多的心理健康问题，特别是儿童和青少年的心理健康问题，中国国家卫生健康委员会将在2025年至2027年期间解决心理健康服务方面的差距。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:57:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-health-commission-narrow-gaps-mental-health-services-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道新年首次中国“战斗巡逻”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-chinese-combat-patrol-new-year-2025-01-02/</link><description>在台湾总统赖清德再次表示愿意与北京对话后，台湾国防部周四表示，中国战机和军舰已进行新年首次环岛“战斗巡逻”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 05:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-first-chinese-combat-patrol-new-year-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普2.0风险加剧，欧洲、亚洲和美国工厂2024年末表现疲弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asias-factories-end-2024-weak-footing-trump-20-risks-mount-2025-01-02/</link><description>亚洲、欧洲和美国的工厂活动在 2024 年结束时表现疲软，原因是唐纳德·特朗普连任总统导致贸易风险不断加大，加上中国经济复苏脆弱，新年预期恶化。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 03:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asias-factories-end-2024-weak-footing-trump-20-risks-mount-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国工厂活动增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/growth-chinas-factory-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-01-02/</link><description>周四的一项私营部门调查显示，由于对贸易前景的担忧导致出口订单下降，整体销售受到抑制，中国12月份工厂活动有所增长，但增速低于预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 01:47:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/growth-chinas-factory-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>随着投资者假期后回归，中国乐观情绪推动油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-investors-return-holidays-eye-china-recovery-2025-01-02/</link><description>在习近平主席承诺促进增长后，投资者对中国经济和燃料需求持乐观态度，周四油价上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 01:34:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-investors-return-holidays-eye-china-recovery-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>《华盛顿邮报》称中国对美国财政部的黑客攻击违反了制裁办公室</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-treasurys-sanctions-office-hacked-by-chinese-government-washington-post-2025-01-02/</link><description>据《华盛顿邮报》周三报道，中国政府黑客入侵了负责管理经济制裁的美国财政部办公室，并确定了本周早些时候披露的财政部网络攻击目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 00:01:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-treasurys-sanctions-office-hacked-by-chinese-government-washington-post-2025-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>普京命令俄罗斯政府和顶级银行与中国发展人工智能合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/putin-orders-russian-government-top-bank-develop-ai-cooperation-with-china-2025-01-01/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已命令俄罗斯政府和该国最大的银行俄罗斯联邦储蓄银行与中国在人工智能领域建立合作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 13:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/putin-orders-russian-government-top-bank-develop-ai-cooperation-with-china-2025-01-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>